title: BigFish - Paparazzi - Hidden Object - Requested [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Paparazzi

Get a glimpse into the bizarre world of tabloid newspapers 
as you travel the country on the trail of hot gossip and 
absurd news stories. Use your eyes and quick reflexes to 
capture photos of strange subjects and sell them to humorous 
tabloid newspapers for valuable cash. Join the Paparazzi!

    * 10 photo assignments.
    * 15 unique locations.
    * Mini-games.
